"{\"uid\": \"news3lv.com-news-local-boulder-city-local-on-olympic-team-is-ready-to-take-a-shot-at-the-gold\", \"text\": \"Now  47\\u00b0  Wed  59\\u00b0  Thu  56\\u00b0  President Donald Trump holds his 9th cabinet meeting at the White House.  byWarren Tennyson  LAS VEGAS (KSNV) -One of our locals Alexis Lagan from Boulder City just touched down inParistoday.  Lagan is once again shooting for gold. She competed on the U.S. Shooting team back in 2021 at the Tokyo Olympics.  She took to social media to show off the athlete welcome experience and also show off all her fun new gear for this year's games.  She will be representing the United States in the air pistol events.  We can not wait to cheer her and  all the other amazing athletes on for their quest for gold.  2025Sinclair, Inc.\"}"